OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells. There
OL,7,Fwill be a scattering of showers, these
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy in the west.
OL,9,FShowers dying out later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Blustery southwesterly
OL,11,Fwinds in the northwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will spread northeast
OL,14,Fthis evening, although light and
OL,15,Fpatchy in the east. Further outbreaks
OL,16,Fof rain overnight, mainly across the
OL,17,Fwest where it will turn persistent
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
