OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain will clear
OL,6,Faway northeast through the morning.
OL,7,FThen turning brighter with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers, occasionally heavy in the
OL,9,Fwest later. Fresh to strong
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,13,Fcloudy with showers on Saturday, windy
OL,14,Fat first. Drier on Sunday but still a
OL,15,Ffew light showers around. Chance of
OL,16,Fsome showery rain on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
